Investing in Great Global Businessesfor the Long-Term









 Polen Capital Focus Global Growth Fund (UCITS)
Polen Capital’s Focus Global Growth strategy was launched in a UCITS format on 29th January 2015 with the USD classes; other UCITS classes have been activated as demand arises.
“The Polen Capital Focus Global Growth Fund” is marketed outside the United States to institutional and professional investors and, where appropriate, properly accredited or high net worth investors.  Any prospective investor must qualify below before accessing the marketing materials.
This strategy and all related funds are managed by Julian Pick, the Portfolio Manager, who identifies and invests into global ‘large cap’ companies that meet Polen’s established investment philosophy.  The Global Growth strategy is an extension of the established Focus Growth strategy into a global universe of companies.

