Investing in Great Global Businessesfor the Long-Term







 Polen Growth Fund (U.S. Mutual Fund)
Launched in 2010, the Polen Growth Fund seeks to achieve long-term growth of capital with an active Investment Process that relies on in-depth research to uncover competitively-advantaged companies that meet our Investment Criteria.
The Polen Growth Fund, co-managed by Dan Davidowitz and Damon Ficklin in a similar manner to our Focus Growth SMA, invests in a focused portfolio of Large Cap Growth companies that have a sustainable competitive advantage and are less likely to ebb and flow with market events.

