Capital Markets

Company Overview of Polen Capital Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Polen Capital Management, LLC is an employee owned investment manager. It primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. The firm also caters to  individuals, investment companies, family offices, endowments and foundations, pension and profit sharing plans, other pooled investment vehicles, corporations, state or municipal government entities, and public funds. It manages separate client-focused equity portfolios. The firm also manages limited partnerships and offshore funds for its clients. It also launches and manages equity mutual funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity markets of the United States. It invests in growth stocks of large-cap companies t...
Polen Capital Management, LLC is an employee owned investment manager. It primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. The firm also caters to  individuals, investment companies, family offices, endowments and foundations, pension and profit sharing plans, other pooled investment vehicles, corporations, state or municipal government entities, and public funds. It manages separate client-focused equity portfolios. The firm also manages limited partnerships and offshore funds for its clients. It also launches and manages equity mutual funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity markets of the United States. It invests in growth stocks of large-cap companies to create its portfolios. The firm benchmarks the performance of its portfolios against the S&P 500 Index and  Russell 1000. It employs a fundamental analysis combined with bottom up stock picking approach to make its investments. Polen Capital Management, LLC was founded in 1979, and is based in Boca Raton, Florida.
Detailed Description


