 Career History



Office Administrator

                                    Current                


Polen Capital Management LLC


                  Polen Capital Management (PCM) employs disciplined, bottom-up, concentrated US, Global and International equity investment strategies that focus on high-quality, large-cap growth investments. The Polen Focus Growth strategy invests in a portfolio of companies PCM believes can deliver mid-teens earnings per share growth over the next 5 years while incurring only moderate risk. The strategy invests in a concentrated portfolio of primarily large-cap, US common stocks with sustainable competitive advantages. The Polen Growth Fund is a US, large-cap US growth fund that emphasizes sustainable earnings growth and focuses on companies with high returns on capital and double digit earnings growth. It is a concentrated portfolio of approximately 30 high-quality growth companies with low portfolio turnover and long-term holding periods.PCM's Global Growth strategy is similar to their Focus Growth strategy, but with adjustments to compensate for fundamental and macro-economic influences that may have a greater effect on the relative performance of foreign stocks than domestic issues. It invests in a concentrated portfolio of outstanding US and international businesses with competitive advantages and the potential for sustained superior growth. The Polen Global Growth Fund emphasizes sustainable earnings growth and focuses on companies with high returns on capital and double digit earnings growth. It is a concentrated portfolio of approximately 30 high-quality growth companies with low portfolio turnover and long-term holding periods.The Polen International Growth strategy applies the same philosophy as the Focus Growth and Global Growth portfolios, but invests exclusively in businesses domiciled outside of the US. Adjustments are made to compensate for macro-economic and country-specific influences that can impact the relative performance of foreign stocks. The strategy invests in a concentrated portfolio of primarily large-cap, non-US businesses with competitive advantages and the potential for sustained superior growth. The Polen Capital International Growth Fund seeks to achieve long-term growth of capital with with PCM's \"\"Active Share Investment Process\"\" that relies on in-depth research to uncover competitively-advantaged companies that meet their disciplined investment criteria.                





 Other Affiliations




              Denise Avila is affiliated with
                            Polen Capital Management LLC.
            





