 People
Attracting, developing and retaining talent is the key factor to the long-term growth of the firm.
Our Team
Polen Capital is led by a talented team of experienced professionals who have been directly responsible for the dynamic growth of the firm. As investors in our strategies, each member's interests are directly aligned with our clients and their investments. Our team is focused on implementing our clearly defined Investment Process and providing investing excellence with personalized customer service.




