Polen Capital is a global, independently-owned equity boutique serving institutional investors, financial professionals and high net worth individuals with a focus on long-term growth and superior service.




 Our Philosophy
At Polen Capital, we believe earnings growth is the primary driver of long-term stock appreciation. We strive to identify the highest quality companies, holding them for the long-term and letting the businesses do what they do best - work to achieve sustainable above-average growth.




 Our Strategies
Our strategies utilize an innovative bottom-up, concentrated approach to growth stock investing, led by experienced teams of investment professionals.  Our Investment Process is active, disciplined, time-tested, and repeatable.




